Tiny_CompressImages::TinyPNG: Tiny_CompressImages::TinyPNG uses smart lossy compression techniques to reduce the file size of your PNG files. Tiny_CompressImages::TinyPNG: Tiny_CompressImages::PNG is useful because it's the only widely supported format that can store partially transparent images.
